notesStmt.note: Red stamp on first leaf of each physical volume: "Matsuura zōsho"? Character "matsu" may be variant Morohashi 14625.

msContents.summary: Manuscript of a political and economic text, in an unidentified hand, originally in ten volumes bound as five but now bound together in a single volume. Preface has authorial attribution "Dazai junsho."

supportDesc.extent: 10 volumes in 5 (50, 37, 44, 43, 55 double leaves) in 1 : 235 x 160 (175 x 115) mm bound to 245 x 182 mm

collation.p: Paper, ii (20th-century) + 50 double leaves + 37 double leaves + 44 double leaves + 43 double leaves + 55 double leaves + ii (20th century); each of the 5 component volumes still has its original cover.
